[I] Yet another shell

[T] Yash, yet another shell, is a POSIX-compliant command line shell written in
[T] C99 (ISO/IEC 9899:1999). Yash is intended to be the most POSIX-compliant
[T] shell in the world while supporting features for daily interactive and
[T] scripting use.

[U] https://github.com/magicant/yash/

[A] Yash Authors
